程序包 <Unnamed>

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Compare  
    ExceptionManager
    A exception manager for the class parser.
    Parser
    This is a Parser which can change expression from infix to postfix, the expression doesn't have '(', ')' , and its operator of expression only has '+' and '-', and operand of expression is a digit number which means '0'-'9'.
    Parser_Loop
    It is a parser which is using loop method
    Parser_Recursive
    It is a parser which is using recursive method
    Postfix
    It is the main function for project Postfix.
    ProduceInfix
    This class can produce an random infix expression, it may be used for testing the Parser is correct, and compare the efficiency between Parser_Loop and Parser_Recursive
